      <title>消息人士稱，必和必拓堅稱任何收購都必須納入英美資源集團的南非資產</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/bhp-insists-anglo-americans-south-african-assets-must-go-any-takeover-sources-2024-05-07/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[了解必和必拓想法的投資者表示，必和必拓計劃剝離其目標英美資源集團的南非資產，這是擬議收購背後策略的關鍵，預計將成為任何修訂報價的一部分。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/bhp-insists-anglo-americans-south-african-assets-must-go-any-takeover-sources-2024-05-07/</guid>
