      <title>隨著電動車炒作降溫，豐田將從混合動力車中獲得收益提升</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/toyota-get-an-earnings-lift-hybrids-ev-hype-cools-2024-05-07/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[當豐田汽車週三公佈年度收益時，預計混合動力車的需求將大幅提振，這表明隨著電池電動車的炒作降溫，這家全球最暢銷的汽車製造商將如何受益。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/toyota-get-an-earnings-lift-hybrids-ev-hype-cools-2024-05-07/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 07 May 2024 07:01:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
